# Browser session for the main Simple web/browser surface.
#
# Scope:
# - page lifecycle state: begin/open/commit/stop/reload/back/forward
# - HTML body rendering through the existing browser renderer
# - inline script execution through the shared JS runtime
# - minimal browser-like host globals: window/document/location/navigator/chrome
#
# Non-goals:
# - network-backed HTTP/HTTPS navigation beyond the request/response pump
# - full DOM API parity
# - full CSS/browser parity beyond inline/link/@import preservation
#
# Split files (all in std.gc_async_mut.web):
# - browser_session_url.spl       — URL utilities and find_text
# - browser_session_storage.spl   — storage helpers, user-agent strings, pair helpers
# - browser_session_cookies.spl   — cookie management, split_text/join_text
# - browser_session_html.spl      — HTML/text utils, stylesheet handling
# - browser_session_modules.spl   — JS module transform (core)
# - browser_session_modules_helpers.spl — JS module helpers, text utilities
# - browser_session_runtime.spl   — impl BrowserSession: eval/render/sync methods
# - browser_session_loading.spl   — impl BrowserSession: stylesheet/script loading

